        {
            "title": "恒科指升超2%，站上4900點！京東、阿里、百度領升科網股",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/99qoMVSdl04fu0CUthAM2A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC5E1KQ_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周三，4月15日，港股市場普升，恒生科技指數升超2%，站上4900點！大型科技股領升，京東 (HK:9618)飆升6%，攜程、阿里巴巴-SW (HK:9988)、百度升超4%，b站、快手升超3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息面上，國內大模型與AI應用生態加速落地，騰訊QCLAW開啟公測、阿里Wan2.7-Image/Video視頻生成模型、火山引擎Seedance 2.0、阿里雲JVS Claw移動端App等密集發佈。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6928374d-3c85-3e8f-a3d5-340a13fb7b2b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">港股硬科技2025年年報業績表現穩健，據統計，中證港股通資訊技術綜合指數52只成份股中41家實現歸母淨利潤同比正增長，其中12家更是實現100%以上翻倍增長。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">開源證券認為，國產模型在視頻生成/Coding/Agent等方面的持續進步，將繼續拉動模型Token、算力雲需求高增，並推動AI廣告/漫劇等AI應用商業化加速。此外，進入一季報披露視窗，在AI商業化提速與內卷競爭熄火的雙重驅動下，多個互聯網龍頭企業業績展望積極。</p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>美股財報季來襲，</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>Warren AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>一鍵解讀數據！現在</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"772\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4tzjjllQsspxWag2E6dv_w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc3Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/0ecb8762545a775c4cb0e5a138b574b5\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><span><br/></span></p></blockquote></div>",
